org.chronos.chronograph.api

Interface ChronoGraphFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChronoGraphFactoryImpl

    public interface ChronoGraphFactory
    The graph factory is responsible for creating new ChronoGraph instances.

    You can use the INSTANCE constant directly, or alternatively use ChronoGraph.FACTORY to get access to the singleton instance of this class.
